nodes.text: This warehouse was a storage facility that was located in the city New Nystao, on the planet Wayland. During the time of the New Republic, the smuggler Arthen Brutt rented the warehouse and stored in it a number of artifacts that he had recovered from Mount Tantiss, a former storehouse of Emperor Palpatine. In about 12 ABY, the rogue Jedi Dal Konur broke into the warehouse and stole a number of items of weaponry, including a lightsaber and some Droideka battle droids.
